6.21	Gylfi_Sigur%C3%B0sson	Gylfi Sigurðsson	Gylfi Þór Sigurðsson (born 8 September 1989) is an Icelandic footballer who plays for Swansea City, on loan from 1899 Hoffenheim, as a central attacking midfielder. He is a specialist on set-pieces and possesses great long-range shooting ability. He has been voted player of the season for two consecutive seasons for Reading and Hoffenheim respectively.	
